{"header":{"word":"דַּ֫עַת","entry":3823,"letter":"י","strongs":1847,"page":395},"definitions":[{"title":"Def","body":" &#134; [[דַּ֫עַת]] ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"n.f.","body":":Ps 139:6, Da 12:4 (m. Pr 2:10, Pr 14:6, poss. Job 33:3 Ew:&#167;174 g) knowledge (prop. Inf., which appears clearly Ge 2:9, Ge 2:17, Je 22:16)&#8212;abs. [[דַּ֫עַת]] Ge 2:9 + 35 t.; [[דָָּעַת]] Jos 20:3 + 35 t.; cstr. [[דַּ֫עַת]] Nu 24:16 + 10 t.; sf. [[דַּעְתִּי]] Pr 22:17; [[דַּעְתְְּ]] Job 10:7; [[דַּעְתֵח]] Is 47:10; [[דַּעְתּוֹ]] Pr 3:20, Is 53:11; [[דַּעְתְּכֶם]] Job 13:2; [[דַּעְתָּם]] Is 44:25; &#8212;","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"1. a.","body":" knowledge, perception in phrase &#180;[[בִּבְלִי ד]] De 4:42 = unintenionally, De 19:4, Jos 20:3 (where P's synonym is [[בִּשְׁגׇגׇה]] v:Jos 20:3, v:Jos 20:9, cf. Nu 35:11, Nu 35:15), v:Nu 35:5; without knowing &#180;[[מִבְּלִי ד]] Is 5:13 ( = before they knew it, suddenly). ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"b.","body":" = skill (in work-manship) Ex 31:3, Ex 35:31 (both P; both &#8214;[[תְּבוּנׇה]] and [[חָכְמָה]]), 1Ki 7:14 (sq. inf.); creative skill Is 40:14 (&#8214;[[אׂרַח מִשְׁפָּט]], [[דֶּרֶח תְּכוּנוֹת]]). ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"c.","body":" of proph. knowledge [[עליון]] &#180;[[יׁדֵעַ ד]] Nu 24:16 (JE), cf. Ps 19:3. ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"d.","body":" esp. knowledge with moral quality Ge 2:9, Ge 2:17 (J; in both verbal force, [[מוֹב וׇרַע]] &#180;[[הַדּ]] the knowing good and evil). ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"e.","body":" knowledge possessed by God Job 10:7, Ps 139:6, Pr 3:20 (&#8214;[[חָכְמָה]] and [[תְּבוּנׇה]]), Pr 21:12; taught by God to men Ps 94:10, Ps 119:66 (&#8214;[[טוּב טַעַם]]), Pr 2:6 (&#8214;[[תְּבוּנׇה]] and [[חָכְמָה]]). ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"f.","body":" [[דַּעַת־רוּחַ]] = windy (unreal) knowledge Job 15:2. ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"2.","body":" esp. in WisdLt = discernment, understanding, wisdom: ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"a.","body":" Job 13:2, Job 33:3 ([[שְׂפָתַי]] &#180;[[ד]]), [[לאׁ בְּדַעַת]] Job 34:35(&#8214;[[חכמה]]), Pr 8:9, Pr 8:10 (&#8214;[[מוסר]]), Pr 10:4, Pr 11:9, Pr 18:15, Pr 18:15, Pr 22:12, Pr 29:7, cf. Is 32:4, Is 53:11, Je 10:14 = Je 51:17; [[בבלי דעת]] Job 35:16, Job 36:12; &#180;[[בלי ד]] Job 38:2, Job 42:3, &#180;[[בְּלאׁ ד]] Pr 19:2; &#8214;[[תְּבוּנׇה]] Pr 17:27, Is 44:19; &#180;[[ת]] + [[חכמה]] Pr 24:4, &#8214;[[מְזִמָּה]] Pr 1:4, Pr 5:2; [[מְזִמּוֹת]] &#180;[[ד]] Pr 8:12; &#8214; vb. [[עָרַם]] Pr 19:25; &#8214;[[מׂחֵעוֹת]] Pr 22:20; &#8214;[[מוּסָר]] Pr 12:1, Pr 19:27, Pr 23:12; &#8214;[[תּוֹרָה]] Mal 2:7; &#8214;[[חכמה]] Pr 14:6, Ec 1:16, Ec 1:18, Ec 2:21, Ec 2:26, Ec 7:12, Ec 9:10: connected with [[חָכָם]] Pr 21:11, Ec 12:9; [[דברי חכמים]] Pr 22:17; Is 33:6 ([[חכמת]]) Is 44:25 ([[חכמים]]); wisdom of magicians Is 47:10, Da 1:4 (&#8214;[[חָכְמָה]] and [[מַדָּע]]). ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"b.","body":" in highest sense, knowledge of God (incl. obedience) Ho 4:1, Ho 4:6 ([[מִבְּלִי הַדַּעַת]]), v:Ho 4:6, Ho 6:6, Job 21:14, Pr 2:5 (&#8214;&#180;[[יראת י]]), so Is 11:2, Is 58:2, Je 22:16 (verbal force, c. acc.), Pr 9:10 ([[קדשׁים]] &#180;[[ד]], &#8214;&#180;[[יראת י]]), Pr 30:3 (id., &#8214;[[חָכְמָה]]); v. also &#180;[[ראשׁית ד]] &#180;[[יִרְאַת י]] Pr 1:7 (&#8214;[[חָכְמָה מוּסָר]]), v:Pr 1:22, v:Pr 1:29 (&#8214;&#180;[[יִרְאַת י]]) Pr 2:10 (&#8214;[[חָכְמָה]]). ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"c.","body":" opp. [[אִוֶּלֶת]] Pr 12:23, Pr 13:16, Pr 14:18, Pr 15:2 cf. v:Pr 15:7, also v:Pr 15:14. ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"d.","body":" &#180;[[שִׂפְתֵי־ד]] Pr 14:7, Pr 20:15; &#180;[[אישׁ ד]] Pr 24:5 (&#8214;[[גֶּבֶר חָכָם]]).&#8212;Da 12:4 is dub.; LXX Bev rd. [[ותרכה הָרָעׂת]].\r","content":"definition","show":"block"}],"notes":"","etymology":[],"morphology":[]}